A POModoro Activities Register

initial scope:
  - Tasks
    . Creation, editing, deleting, canceling, rejecting;
    . Scheduling, re-scheduling, association with pomodoro, estimating (in pomodoros);
    . associating with projects, dependency..

  - Timer
    . Pomodoro: creation, starting, canceling, task association, tag association;
    . Short break: starting, canceling (?);
    . Longer break: starting, calceling (?).
    . Internal and external interruptions registering.

  - Reports
    . Pomodoros by time, by tag, by project;
    . Interruptions by of time, by project;
    . Estimates x real pomodoros.
